Jurgen Klopp: &quot;Divock Origi played really good games when he started, Barcelona and Everton are good examples. There are so many differences between starting and coming off the bench.&quot; #awlfc [lfc]<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It's about coming in, finding rhythm - there are plenty of differences but that is mostly personal. It is a learning process. There is a lot of pressure involved - that's why sometimes players perform under their level.&quot;

